high_descs: Walk few steps then turn to your right walk towards the table
Pick up the middle knife below the tomato on the table
Turn to your left and head to the stove
Put the knife in the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with the knife
Turn to your right and go to the right side of the sink counter above the dishwasher
Put down the pan with the knife on the sink counter
anns.task_desc: Put pan with knife on the sink counter

high_descs: Move to the table to the right of the fridge
Pick up up a knife from the table
move to the stove to the left of the sink
put the knife on a pan on the stove
pick up the pan from the stove
move to the counter to the right of the sink
put the pan on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife on it on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk towards the white counter against the wall.
Pick up the knife closest to the edge of the counter, in front of the tomato.
Turn to your left and walk past the refrigerator, to the stove.
Place the knife in the fry pan that is on the rear, left side of the stove.
Pick up the fry pan with the knife inside it.
Turn to your right, and walk to the kitchen counter that in on the right side of the sink, above the dishwasher.
Set the fry pan with the knife inside on the counter behind and to the left of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a fry pan with a knife inside it on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: turn right to the white table
grab the knife on the right
turn around, walk to the stove
put the knife in the rear left pan
take the pan from the stove
turn right to the counter by the sink
put down the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: put the knife in the rear left pan, move the pan to the counter by the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk to table that contains a tomato and knives.
Pick up knife directly below the tomato on the table.
Turn to left, go to stove with pot on the right lower burner.
Place knife in pan on left upper burner.
Pick up pan with knife in it.
Turn to right, move to microwave.  Turn left towards counter with sponge in front of you.
Place pan on counter, to the right of sink, with the sponge to it's left lower side.
anns.task_desc: Put knife in pan, move pan near the sink.
